FBIS4-49778 "drchi091_d_94004" FBIS-CHI-94-091 Daily Report 10 May 1994 Northeast Asia Li Tieying Receives DPRK Publications Official Li Tieying Receives DPRK Publications Official OW1005130494 Beijing XINHUA in English 1128 GMT 10 May 94 OW1005130494 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, May 10 (XINHUA) -- Li Tieying, Chinese State Councillor and minister in charge of the state commission for restructuring the economy, met here today with Yi Pong-su, general director of the bureau of publication of the Democratic People's Republic of Korea (DPRK). The DPRK visitors are here as guests of the Press and Publication Administration of China.
